Data Collection Method: Jamar Count Boards (D4-5824 & D-585)
1) Wake Christian Academy and Wake Tech Community College are
located in the immediate vicinity of the intersection. Both
schools were notified and in session on the day of the count.
2) Pedestrians were observed and counted, none were disabled.
3) The NB approach grade is -1%, SB is 1% and EB is -2%.
4) No highway construction was observed within a ¼ mile radius.
5) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of
6) Counters took a break from 12:45 to 1:15 PM and from 4:30 to
4:45 PM. Data for these periods was interpolated.
7) The counters did not have any additional notes.
